This is an implementation of SurfLab's BezierView using WebGL and Three.js

http://www.cise.ufl.edu/research/SurfLab/bview/

Current version:
Shayan development version: http://dl.dropbox.com/u/6665854/BezierView/BezierView.html
Saleh development version: http://www.cise.ufl.edu/~saleh/BezierView/

Controls:
-Use mouse buttons to rotate, pan and zoom
-'c' to toggle control mesh, 'p' to toggle patches
